quot;font-size: 8px&quot;&gt;auditor should agree on the terms of the audit engagement with &lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px&quot;&gt;the bank before beginning&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;6.&amp;nbsp; Initial Engagements:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px&quot;&gt;perform procedures as per SA 510&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;7. &amp;nbsp; Assessment of Engagement Risk: &lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px&quot;&gt;assessment of engagement risk is a should be done prior to the acceptance &lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px&quot;&gt;of anaudit engagement since it affects decision of &lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px&quot;&gt;accepting the engagement and planning&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;8.&amp;nbsp; Understanding the Bank and its Environment:&amp;nbsp; &lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 8px&quot;&gt;as per SA 315&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
